@node Options "Editor Options"

  Name          HotKey    Description
  -----------------------------------
  "3 Strings"   P+TAB     Use the TAB key to select which string to edit.

  Choose Font   F         Choose font, style, colour, & other attributes.
  Screen Mode   M         Selects display mode.  Font requester might
                          make available more colours than you have
                          choosen for the screen's depth!

  Save          S         Saves preferences.
  Cancel        C         Exit/Cancel without saving.
  Priority      P         Only change if you are experienced with AmigaDOS!

  Music         .         Music module file requester.

@endnode
